Path Recruitment Message 4

Date: 02/05/2023

Greetings from The Path. We are a team of mutated apes, led by the visionary Mega Gold, who are dedicated to creating a better future for all mutants. As we continue our recruitment drive, we would like to extend an invitation to you to join us on this journey.

Our cause is noble, our mission is clear, and we believe that with your help, we can make a real impact in the world. So, without further ado, we present to you our recruitment message, in rhyme.

Join The Path, it's time to take flight,
With Mega Gold, we'll win this fight,
Against Doc Gibbons, we'll make a stand,
For a brighter future, hand in hand.

Together we'll soar, we'll reach new heights,
With The Path, our future shines so bright,
So come on, join us, be a part,
Of a brighter tomorrow, from the start.

Together, we are unstoppable.

Join us and be a part of The Path.
